<help general bug>

This is for reporting any bugs, typos or other technical problems with
the MUD.  It is extremely helpful to the Builders and Coders.  The
command automatically logs the room you are in and your name,
to save us all some time!

syntax:  bug [message_txt]
syntax:  typo [message_txt]

example:  bug Are you supposed to spell chameleon with a K??

<color=red>
See Also:  idea buglist idealist
</color>
Note:  This command, as well as 'idea', notes who you are and what room
       you are in.  This should help make your message concise.
</help>
